metadata.name: Cosmic Egg
metadata.description:
‘Cosmic Egg’ is a representation of the element of water and the origins of life in the Universe. The concept of the “cosmic egg” is a mythological motif found in the cosmogonies of many cultures. It symbolize the unification of two complementary principles from which life or existence, in its most fundamental philosophical sense, emerges.

Year 2022
Medium: 1080p HEVC mp4 video 
Technique: Mixed Media (physical painting captured on video, digitally composited, edited and shaped into the final piece)
Duration: 02:09
Dimensions 1920pixels x 1080pixels
Unique 1/1

Buyer will have access to full 4k hi-def video file of Cosmic Egg and 3 exclusive original  still artworks related to this Collection.
